'''Kanada''' ni igihugu kinini cyane giherereye mu gice cyo mu majyaruguru y’umugabane wa [[Amerika ya Ruguru]]. Gikikijwe n’inyanja ya [[Atalantika]] mu burasirazuba, inyanja ya [[Pasifika]] mu burengerazuba n’inyanja ya [[Arikitika]] mu majyaruguru. Nicyo gihugu cya kabiri kinini ku isi mu buso (''total area'')nyuma y’u Burusiya, aho gifite ubuso bwa [[kilometero kare]] 9,984,670. Kanada ihana imbibe na [[Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika]] mu majyepfo no mu majyaruguru y’uburengerazuba, ukaba ariwo mupaka muremure ku isi.

Ubusanzwe Kanada yari ituwe n’abasangwabutaka kugera mu kinyejana cya 15 ubwo [[abafaransa]] n’[[abongereza]] bazaga kureba uko hameze. Nyuma baje kuhatura rero, mu nkengero za Atalantika. Abo basangwabutaka baje gushegeshwa bikomeye n’indwara zari ziturutse i [[Burayi]], ubu hasigaye mbarwa.

== Amateka ==
Mu mwaka wa [[1763]] abafaransa baretse colonies zose bari bafite muri Amerika ya ruguru, nyuma y’intambara yiswe '"Seven Years' War". Mu mwaka w’ 1867, Kanada yahinduwe intara ifite ubwigenge bucagase, icibwamo intara 4, aha ni naho hatangiriye ukwigenga gusumbyeho, byatumye Kanada itacyometse cyane ku [[Bwongereza]]. Mu mwaka wa [[1919]], Kanada yinjiye muri Société des Nations (League of Nations) nk’igihugu ukwacyo kitari mu Bwongereza, naho mu mwaka wa 1945, Kanada iba kimwe mu bihugu byashinze Loni.

== Intara na teritwari ==
[[File:Political map of Canada.png|thumb|250px|<font color="green">Ikarita yerekana intara na teritwari za Kanada.</font>]]
Kuri ubu Kanada igizwe n’intara 10 arizo: Ontario,Québec, Alberta, Nova Scottia, New Brunswick, Manitoba, British Columbia, Prince Edward Island, Saskatchewan na Newfoundland and Labrador. Kanada kandi igizwe na [[teritwari]] 3 (''territories'')

== Ibendera rya Kanada ==
[[File:Flag of Canada.svg|thumb|left|100px|<font color="green">Ibendera rya Kanada</font>]]
Ibendera rya Kanada rizwi cyane, rikaba ari umweru n’umutuku. Hagati harimo ishusho ry’ikibabi cy’igiti cyitwa érable ushobora gusanga henshi muri icyo gihugu, kikaba cyinatanga umutobe uryoshye (''sirop d'érable'').

